            <h3>QPs currently manage reservations through a mix of portal emails, platform messages, texting, templates, and manual planning. Phase 1 focuses on reducing this operational fragmentation.</h3>

            <h4><span class="fontWeight500">Symptom/current situation:</span> Provider manage business at night, delivery during the day</h4>
            <h4><span class="fontWeight500">Provider growth:</span> Active provider is bout 3000-4000, never fully grow</h4>
            <h4><span class="fontWeight500">Goal:</span>The goal is build a provider app to help them manage daily business on the goal by reusing current web portal features that can launch faster</h4>
            <h3>Business owners want to have more control over their business:</h3>

            <div class="marginLeft">
              <h5>· Rounting, location</h5>
              <h5>· Availability</h5>
              <h5>· Communication</h5>
            </div>

