            <h3>How QPs actually manage communication.</h3>
            <h3>Stephanie’s workflow:</h3>
            <div class="marginLeft">
              <h5>· email as alert feed</h5>
              <h5>· texting as reliable coordination</h5>
              <h5>· templates in Google Keep</h5>
              <h5>· weekly/night/weekend planning</h5>
              <h5>· reservation timing as primary scan object</h5>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="Grid Grid--gutters Grid--full Grid--gutter">
        <div class="Grid-cell">
          <div class="element">
            <h4 class="fontWeight400 GreyBg400 GreyBg200 border-radius paddingXS">💡 Key insight: Reservation is the primary object. Communication is secondary.</h4>
          </div>
