            <h4>Turn insights into principles:</h4>
            <div class="marginLeft">
              <h5>· Anchor communication to reservations</h5>
              <h5>· Separate human messages from operational alerts</h5>
              <h5>· Prioritize urgency over chronology</h5>
              <h5>· Support real channels instead of pretending everything stays in-app</h5>
              <h5>· Reduce QP mental load during active reservations</h5>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>
